      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXPRESSING (8) finished second last start over 2185m at this track, beaten a nose. That was an improvement on the unplaced effort at Gloucester Park the run before. Drawn to enjoy an economical run and might sweat on the sprint lane. Leading hope if things go her way. ROCKABILLY JOE (1) is at the track for the first time. By Fly Like An Eagle and hails from the Dylan Egerton-Green stable. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Looks to have some talent based on a recent trial win. Capable of taking this out. THE BELL HUEY (7) lines up for the first time. By Fly Like An Eagle and hails from the Sonia Zucchiatti stable. Has to contend with a very wide draw. Makes plenty of appeal. RACKETEERS DREAM (3) was beaten 16 metres on debut four months ago over 1730m at Gloucester Park. First-up since that run and has plenty of scope for improvement.",
